title: Ep. - 405 - EDDIE LUCAS FROM BELOW DECK HOUSE OF SECRETS: THE BURARI DEATHS
description:
Eddie Lucas from Bravo’s Below Deck, which profiles a group of young people who work aboard yachts. The new season begins this week.

 

Reality TV Producer and Podcast Host Chris DeRosa helps Kate review House of Secrets: The Burari Deaths on Netflix, a three part docuseries examining the deaths of 11 members of an Indian family.
